item.title: 【General Music Discussion】Taylor Swift - She needs to release the audio from the Eras tour :
item.description:
I wouldn't say I'm the biggest Taylor Swift fan - I Love the 1989 album and can listen to most of the others :
But, I went and saw the eras tour movie twice ( IT is amazing ).
Then, I went back and listened to some of the songs that really stood out to me in the film & they sound so laid back on CD compared to the power of them Live in Concert.
Her Voice even seems more powerful etc Live in concert compared to her CD's.
Just My Opinion :
So, Hopefully the audio gets released as well as the Movie :
